history.content:
Robinhood Workshop & Infosession this Friday (10/15)!
Berkeley Investment Group (BIG) and Latinx Business Student Association (LBSA) are excited to co-host a Robinhood Financial Literacy event to provide an introduction to Financial Literacy and its merits.
This will also be a chance for you to learn more about Robinhood's internship and new grad program, how to apply, and get any of your questions answered. As a perk for attending, they will be raffling off Robinhood water bottles!
The event will take place on Zoom, you'll be able to chat and ask any questions you have with the speakers. We're looking forward to seeing you then! Please RSVP at the link below and you will receive the Zoom link 15 minutes prior to the event.
RSVP @ https://tinyurl.com/rhinfofa21
